// Edge case tests for new unit categories
// Test: zero values, aliases, precision, boundary conditions

# Temperature Edge Cases
0 celsius
0 fahrenheit
0 kelvin
-273.15 celsius in kelvin

# Very large values
1000000 watts in megawatts
1000 horsepower in kilowatts

# Very small values  
0.001 kilowatts in watts
0.1 calories in joules

# Alias consistency - Temperature
100 c in f
100 celsius in fahrenheit  
100 degc in degf

# Alias consistency - Speed
60 mps
60 meters per second
100 kph in mph
100 kilometers per hour in miles per hour

# Alias consistency - Energy
1 kj in j
1 kilojoule in joules
100 cal in kcal
100 calories in kilocalories

# Alias consistency - Power
1 kw in w
1 kilowatt in watts
5 hp in kw
5 horsepower in kilowatts

# Mixed arithmetic with same category
(100 celsius + 50 celsius) in fahrenheit
(50 mph + 20 mph) in kph
(1000 joules + 1 kilojoule) in kilojoules
(500 watts + 0.5 kilowatts) in kilowatts

# Chained conversions
100 celsius in fahrenheit in kelvin in celsius

# Fractional quantities
0.5 horsepower in watts
1.5 kilowatts in watts
2.5 kilojoules in calories
